---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <script src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
	<hr>
    <main>
      <h1>Ahww, Hello. How are you?</h1>
      <p>
        Hello and welcome to my web page! As a full-stack developer with a
        passion for mathematics and ethical philosophy, I am excited to share my
        knowledge and experience with you.
      </p>
      With a strong foundation in web development and programming, I have developed
      and deployed numerous applications across various industries. Whether it's
      building robust back-end systems or creating beautiful and responsive front-end
      designs, I am committed to delivering high-quality solutions that exceed expectations.

      <p>
        But it's not just about the technical aspects of development - I also
        believe in using technology for good. My love for ethical philosophy has
        led me to explore how technology can be used to create positive social
        impact. By combining my technical skills with my passion for social
        responsibility, I am dedicated to creating solutions that benefit
        society and the environment.
      </p>
      <p>
        In addition to my technical expertise, I am also deeply passionate about
        mathematics. From numerical analysis to abstract algebra, I love
        exploring the beauty and elegance of mathematical concepts. I believe
        that a strong understanding of mathematics is essential for any
        developer, and I strive to incorporate mathematical thinking into all
        aspects of my work.
      </p>
      <p>
        So, whether you're looking to build a new web application or just want
        to learn more about the intersection of technology and philosophy, I'm
        here to help. Thank you for visiting my page, and I look forward to
        connecting with you!
      </p>
    </main>
	<hr>
    <Footer />
    <script>
      declare global {
        interface Window {
          netlifyIdentity: any;
        }
      }

      if (window.netlifyIdentity) {
        window.netlifyIdentity.on("init", (user: any) => {
          if (!user) {
            window.netlifyIdentity.on("login", () => {
              document.location.href = "/admin/";
            });
          }
        });
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
